text:
Tested on 1.20 and it gives the same positive results as 1.19.14 (same results with and without listener_kwargs).
Reran 1.21 without listener_kwargs and get the same negative results that were obtained using listener_kwargs.
Summary,
- listener_kwargs had no affect on results
- version 1.20 gives positive results that roughly align with actual
- version 1.21 gives negative results
